{"thag1.37:0.1":"Theragatha 1.37 ","thag1.37:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","thag1.37:0.3":"Catutthavagga ","thag1.37:0.4":"Kumaputtasahayakattheragatha ","thag1.37:1.1":"“Nanajanapadam yanti, ","thag1.37:1.2":"Vicaranta asannata; ","thag1.37:1.3":"Samadhinca viradhenti, ","thag1.37:1.4":"Kimsu ratthacariya karissati; ","thag1.37:1.5":"Tasma vineyya sarambham, ","thag1.37:1.6":"Jhayeyya apurakkhato”ti. ","thag1.37:1.7":"… Kumaputtattherassa sahayako thero …. "}